ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of KATHERINE DUDTSCHAK of Toronto, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Gail Asper, O.C., O.M., whose term has expired.
